    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This spell bestows hope and vitality. Choose any number of creatures within range. For the duration, each target gains:</p>\n<ol>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\">Advantage on </span><strong>Wisdom saving</strong> throws and</li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\">Advantage on </span><strong>death saving</strong> throws, and</li>\n<li><strong>Maximum</strong> number of<strong> hit points</strong> possible from any healing.</li>\n</ol>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>FoundryVTT</strong>: Manually target the desired recipients before casting this spell.</p>\n<p>First two effects are automated, third needs to be handled manually.</p>",
